    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 40 min, remove the dish[es] from the oven and pour the<strong> herby stock</strong> all over the potatoes and tomatoes</p><p>Top with your <strong>salmon fillet[s] </strong>(skin side up!)</p><p>Squeeze over the juice<strong> </strong>of the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>and top the salmon with the<strong> reserved</strong> <strong>sliced lemon</strong></p>",
